awd_titl_txt: Group Travel to Attend the 1985 IEEE International Symposiumon Circuits and Systems; Kyoto, Japan; June 5-7, 1985
awd_abstract_narration: Support is provided for attendance at the annual meeting of the IEEE            Circuits and Systems Society, which brings together experts, from all           countries, in the appropriate technical areas.  This year's meeting is          to be held in the Far East, with contacts in Japan and China.  Meetings         will be held between American researchers and their counterparts in             China and Japan.
